6. Records the recomputation count after the batch completes
7. Gets the final value from the calculation
8. Returns all the results in the `BatchExecuteResult` struct

The key insight is that when updates are made within a `reaction::Batch` scope, the reactive system should batch the notifications and only trigger one recomputation of dependent calculations, even when multiple source variables are updated.

